The paper deals with an online learning problem and presents algorithms and regret bounds for the isotonic regression problem. This problem is related to machine learning and optimization, which are covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also involves analysis of different loss functions, which falls under cs.DS and cs.ST. Finally, the paper uses techniques from information theory, which is covered by cs.IT.
